00:50:08,573 --> 00:50:30,443
you know, we're starting to probably get on that border of it's not big enough is not enough. And we talked about that this year, like what is not enough? And I don't know the answer to that. But you know, if we didn't have contractors, we didn't have those 24 contractors come in, and it was just 50 or 54 plows that we have, then

